  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy of autologous epidermal cells suspension
      grafting using a newly developed device named VITICELL® compared to placebo.

      The secondary objective is to evaluate safety of VITICELL® and global satisfaction of patient
      and investigator.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
